    "Initial data statistics Fig. 4 Annual breakdown of the relevant research articlesThis noticeable increase in the number of publications over time, despite some fluctuations, reflects the trendiness of the subject at hand and its growing popularity among researchers.Table 2 displays the top 14 contributing journals as measured by the number of publications, where European Journal of Operational Research (EJOR) was the leading contributor, publishing seven articles, which clearly revels the applicability of Operation Research (OR) tools to handle various modelling and solution aspects of MSPSP.Table 2 Top contributing journals based on publications Journal No.",
